Class ParkingAreaImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.ParkingAreaImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, ParkingArea, Storable
public class ParkingAreaImpl extends BaseObjectImpl implements ParkingArea
A parking area can report the number of available stalls.

Douglas Lau
